

{"id":2050,"date":"2023-03-13T16:25:47","date_gmt":"2023-03-13T09:25:47","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tnt.locdt.site\/staging\/?p=2050"},"modified":"2023-07-20T15:07:07","modified_gmt":"2023-07-20T08:07:07","slug":"top-5-meo-giam-can-hieu-qua","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/top-5-meo-giam-can-hieu-qua\/","title":{"rendered":"Top 5 M\u1eb9o Gi\u1ea3m C\u00e2n Hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 B\u1ea1n C\u00f3 Th\u1ec3 L\u00e0m M\u1ed7i T\u1ed1i"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Top 5 m\u1eb9o gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 <strong>m\u1eb9o gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n<\/strong> hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c th\u00f3i quen tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ng\u1ee7 m\u1ed7i t\u1ed1i l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh <strong>gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n<\/strong> c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch h\u01b0\u1edbng x\u1ea3y ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam khuya. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u00f3i quen ban \u0111\u00eam ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Nh\u1eefng th\u00f3i quen ban \u0111\u00eam gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia th\u00e0nh hai nh\u00f3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">(1) nh\u1eefng th\u00f3i quen \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1ch c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n x\u1eed l\u00fd m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 trong khi b\u1ea1n ng\u1ee7<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">(2) nh\u1eefng th\u00f3i quen gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00eam ngon gi\u1ea5c \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c ng\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp theo.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Khi b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5c, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m sau \u0111\u1ec3 tham gia v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y calo: \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y \u0111\u1ee7 calo trong su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y.\u00a0\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 \u0111i mua s\u1eafm.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i <strong>m\u1eb9o gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n<\/strong> m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ed7i \u0111\u00eam \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt; color: #00a2c4;\"><strong>1. L\u01b0u \u00fd gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ng\u1ee7: Kh\u00f4ng \u0103n qu\u00e1 khuya<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2401 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/khonh-an-qua-khuya-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/khonh-an-qua-khuya-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/khonh-an-qua-khuya-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/khonh-an-qua-khuya-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/khonh-an-qua-khuya-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/khonh-an-qua-khuya-2048x1366.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">B\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0103n v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o, c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd x\u1eed l\u00fd l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo theo c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0103n mu\u1ed9n h\u01a1n v\u00e0o ban \u0111\u00eam c\u0169ng c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0103n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m gi\u00e0u calo h\u01a1n ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0103n v\u00ec \u0111\u00f3i m\u00e0 b\u1edfi v\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111ang bu\u1ed3n ch\u00e1n. Tr\u00e1nh \u0103n khuya tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ng\u1ee7 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 th\u00eam calo m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18pt; color: #00a2c4;\">2. <a style=\"color: #00a2c4;\" href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/loi-ich-cua-viec-tap-the-duc-hang-ngay\/\">T\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c<\/a> \u0111\u00fang gi\u1edd<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2406 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/tap-the-duc-dung-gio-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/tap-the-duc-dung-gio-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/tap-the-duc-dung-gio-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/tap-the-duc-dung-gio-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/tap-the-duc-dung-gio-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/tap-the-duc-dung-gio-2048x1366.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c qu\u00e1 g\u1ea7n gi\u1edd \u0111i ng\u1ee7, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f3 \u0111i v\u00e0o gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y calo trong nh\u1eefng gi\u1edd sau khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c \u0111\u00fang gi\u1edd (ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u mu\u1ed9n ho\u1eb7c \u0111i b\u1ed9 bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i), b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y th\u00eam calo v\u00e0o th\u1eddi gian ng\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><\/h2>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #00a2c4; font-size: 18pt;\">3. Kh\u00f4ng u\u1ed1ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ng\u1ee7<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2408 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/khong-uong-ruou-truoc-khi-ngu-1-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"meo giam can, m\u1eb9o gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/khong-uong-ruou-truoc-khi-ngu-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/khong-uong-ruou-truoc-khi-ngu-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/khong-uong-ruou-truoc-khi-ngu-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/khong-uong-ruou-truoc-khi-ngu-1-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/khong-uong-ruou-truoc-khi-ngu-1-2048x1366.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u00e3 bao nhi\u00eau l\u1ea7n b\u1ea1n t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00eam \u0111i ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 v\u00e0 th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c d\u1eady nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00eam? U\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed3 u\u1ed1ng c\u00f3 c\u1ed3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ng\u1ee7 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f3i quen x\u1ea5u v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do.\u00a0R\u01b0\u1ee3u \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u calo d\u01b0 th\u1eeba, v\u00ec v\u1eady tr\u00e1nh u\u1ed1ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ng\u1ee7 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef cho l\u01b0\u1ee3ng calo t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. R\u01b0\u1ee3u c\u0169ng l\u00e0m gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7, v\u00ec v\u1eady n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n u\u1ed1ng nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ng\u1ee7, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><\/h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #00a2c4; font-size: 18pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><br \/>\n<strong>4.\u00a0\u0110\u1eb7t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u1edf nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 m\u00e1t m\u1ebb n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2399 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/de-phong-ngu-o-nhiet-do-mat-me-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/de-phong-ngu-o-nhiet-do-mat-me-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/de-phong-ngu-o-nhiet-do-mat-me-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/de-phong-ngu-o-nhiet-do-mat-me-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/de-phong-ngu-o-nhiet-do-mat-me-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/03\/de-phong-ngu-o-nhiet-do-mat-me-2048x1366.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u cho th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1ch c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd ch\u1ea5t b\u00e9o v\u00e0 ng\u1ee7 trong ph\u00f2ng m\u00e1t h\u01a1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y nhi\u1ec1u calo h\u01a1n qua \u0111\u00eam.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00f2ng m\u00e1t m\u1ebb s\u1ebd th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 ngon! Theo m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c th\u0103m d\u00f2 c\u1ee7a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.sleepfoundation.org\/bedroom-environment\/best-temperature-for-sleep\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c Gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 Qu\u1ed1c gia<\/a>, ng\u1ee7 trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e1t m\u1ebb l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 ngon v\u00e0 s\u00e2u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Top 5 m\u1eb9o gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, b\u00ed quy\u1ebft gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n, nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n. \u0110\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1eb9o gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c th\u00f3i quen tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ng\u1ee7 m\u1ed7i t\u1ed1i l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":4908,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1,9],"tags":[84,85,86,87],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2050"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2050"}],"version-history":[{"count":60,"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2050\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3208,"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2050\/revisions\/3208"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4908"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2050"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2050"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2050"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}